{
  "stem": "8947.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you had to keep up your hands like this, as long as they wanted.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And every time, if you were unlucky and the guard noticed you, you were beaten up, because you didn't keep your hand up.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "How many times I had the row, this-- this kneeling in the stones?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was the punishment.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So the morning started already with the-- with the torture.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was the first torture.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, then-- then they numbered us also, when you came back from work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Work-- what work was-- I told you what work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "To dig the pits and carry the dead, and drag the corpses-- that was our work in Auschwitz when I was there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They didn't even care anymore to tattoo you, or do anything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't care, because it was just too much work, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Too much.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You never knew how long you are going to be able to do that work, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They didn't tattoo.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I say my thanks to God that they didn't brand me at least, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I don't know, some of my family members who were longer in Auschwitz, they were branded, but I was seven weeks in Auschwitz, you know?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But those seven weeks, I could have died 100 times.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, every single week, three times a week, you had the so-called selection.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I say the death sentence, you faced.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because you had to bash in front of the SS physician.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if he looked at you, and he found that you are not good anymore to work, he pointed you to the left, which was the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Scurvy broke out, scarlet fever, typhus-- it was-- the camp was infested with disease.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Our-- we got foul water, not to speak what we got.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
